WorldStage Newsonline– FCMB Group, Nigeria’s leading financial group has confirmed that Primrose Investments Limited, a related company has purchased 20,000,000 units of its share at N3.33. A notice of insiders dealing on shares filed by Olufunmilayo Adedibu Mrs, Company Secretary said the transaction took place on 31st December 2020. Primrose Development Company (PDC) is a property development company whose roots as real estate developers stretch back over thirty years to its progenitor organizations, Primrose Properties Investment Limited (PPIL) and City Securities Limited.